job.title: C#/.Net Developer - Project Completion
job.description:
We are seeking a skilled C#/.Net developer to assist in completing a project that has already been coded using Visual Studio 2022. The project is at an advanced stage and requires someone with expertise in C#, .Net, and Visual Studio to finalize the remaining tasks. The ideal candidate will have a strong understanding of software development principles, be able to work independently, and have experience in project completion. The primary responsibilities include reviewing and debugging the existing code, implementing necessary changes and enhancements, and ensuring the project meets the required specifications. 

    Required Skills:
    - Proficiency in C# programming
    - In-depth knowledge of .Net framework
    - Experience with Visual Studio 2022
    - Strong problem-solving and debugging skills

    Size: Medium
    Duration: 1-6 Weeks
    Expertise: Intermediate
